{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 13:54:36.009649", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission complete.\n\nSummary:\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): web_server_3\n- Root cause: link_bandwidth_throttling\n\nRationale:\n- Consistently elevated RTT only for web_server_3 from all peers.\n- ip addr statistics shows qdisc netem on eth0, indicating intentional traffic shaping (delay injection), aligning with observed latency inflation.\n- Other servers and network elements normal; no packet loss or routing issues.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1823, "output_tokens": 98, "total_tokens": 1921, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
